Hades/Serpentor/Unitron/Koga Shuko/Anubis/Sixshot:



Hades let Serpentor go by after he had made a nice tunnel, Anubis getting out 
through it somewhat uncomfortably.

He slammed himself against the bottom of the blocked entrance of the cave, 
quickly going upwards, all the remaining rocks blocking the cave collapsing 
into the tunnel, almost filling it completely.  Unitron, Koga Shuko, and 
Sixshot exited the cave, leaving the energon, continuing on with Hades, 
Serpentor, and Anubis for several dozen feet until out of rang eof the 
enrgon, waiting for the others.
